data.description: Absolutely immaculate 2 story home on cul de sac! Tastefully decorated. Large eat in Kitchen with loads of cabinets. Great room has corner fireplace. 3 large bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, main floor laundry, full partially finished base, patio and attached 2 c garage.Master Bed features private bath and walk in closet. Plainfield schools. You will love this beautifully cared for home!
